and conditions of the above-described Mortgage.

personally appeared KALEENA OGO, ASSISTANT VICE PRESIDENT, NS162, LLC, personally known to me (or
proved to me on the basis of satisfactory evidence) to be the person(s) whose name(s) is/are subscribed to the
within instrument and acknowledged to me by means of X physical presence or

instrument the person, or the entity upon behalf of which the person acted, executed the instrument.
